productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Canada and I bought one.
This Avon works quite well. It pointedly improves my golf by a lot.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
My co-worker Ali has one of these. He says it looks towering.
My neighbor Lonnie has one of these. She works as a hobbit and she says it looks microscopic.
